#X text 8 169 Inlet 1 \, grain float: Configure grain length (# of
samples);
#X msg 10 143 grain 360;
#X text 8 189 Inlet 3 \, float: Duration in milliseconds;
#X text 8 179 Inlet 2 \, float: Pitch (1=original pitch);
