AN ERROY ARRAY NO METHOD FOR RETURN;
#X text 9 113 light gate - per row - not needed - 1/0 is starting stopping
it already \, redundancy and clicks!;
#X text 9 68 WHEN WE BANG AND PLAY SAMPLE AND NEXT BANG IS BEFORE THE
