\, EVEN THOUGH WITH BANG IT SOUNDS COOLER;
#X text 9 16 IT WON'T WORK FOR NOW BECAUSE EACH PATCH HAS DIFFERENT
SET OF INPUT CONTROLS \, BUT LATER yes when we HAVE THE SAME SET OF
CTRL;
